{"type":"article","id":23557,"title":"穿越必备：梦回我大清，你会请安吗？","uid":50245,"topics":[85,351,6417,18,163],"contents":"逐词译解学霸请安折，这篇范文建议您熟记于心，好在可汗面前跪立如仪。作者法海是圣祖仁皇帝的表弟，二十三岁就考上进士（没有高考加分），成了罕有的少年翰林。他的名字是fambi (干涸）的连续副动词形式，与金山寺没有关系。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EgooXvvU4AAs2wU?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EgooXvvU4AAs2wU?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EgooXvvU4AAs2wU?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-08-30","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}